LLM_response_editer:
要在 Word 的 "视图 "选项卡下的功能中找到并选中 "网格线 "功能，您需要将鼠标光标移到复选框上并单击它。JSON 操作如下：

```json
[
    {"action_type":"MouseAction","mouse_action_type":"click","mouse_button":"left","mouse_position":{"width":470,"height":100}}
]
```

